<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>-<span class="c5"> يَقْرَأُ فِي الأُولَى بَعْدَ الفَاتِحَةِ:</span> الجُمُعَةَ، وَالثَّانِيَةِ <span class="c2">(١)</span>: المُنَافِقِينَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- وَحَرُمَ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> إِقَامَتُهَا وَعِيدٍ فِي أَكْثَرَ مِنْ مَوْضِعٍ بِبَلَدٍ إِلَّا لِحَاجَةٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَأَقَلُّ السُّنَّةِ بَعْدَهَا:</span> رَكْعَتَانِ،<span class="c5"> وَأَكْثَرُهَا:</span> سِتٌّ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَسُنَّ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- قَبْلَهَا أَرْبَعٌ غَيْرُ رَاتِبَةٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَقِرَاءَةُ الكَهْفِ فِي يَوْمِهَا وَلَيْلَتِهَا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَكَثْرَةُ دُعَاءٍ، وَصَلَاةٍ عَلَى النَّبِيِّ صَلى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- وَغُسْلٌ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَتَنَظُّفٌ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- وَتَطَيُّبٌ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَلُبْسُ بَيَاضٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- وَتَبْكِيرٌ إِلَيْهَا مَاشِياً.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَدُنُوٌّ مِنَ الإِمَامِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في (د): وفي الثانية.<br>(٢) في (أ): ويحرم.</p> </div>